Start
/ Test: Ask via Nostr messaging
- write out 'Nostr Ask Test - Starting...'
- write out 'Waiting for Nostr response (5 min timeout)...'
- ask 'What is your favorite color?' to system, write to %answer%
- write out 'Received answer: %answer%'
- if %answer% is empty, throw error 'No response received'
- write out 'Test PASSED - Channel handler successfully routed ask through Nostr'
